      "id": "PopularPost208208",
      "post_content": "This is amazing. Anything that says \"Lose the game next turn\" (not just pacts, [Final Fortune](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Final Fortune)/[Warrior's Oath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warrior's Oath)/[Last Chance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance), for example) now says \"Skip a turn\". Anything that says \"lose the game now\" reads \"skip the rest of your second main phase\".  \n  \nThis also might as well read \"1, tap, skip your end step: Exile all opponent's spells.\" Combine with [Twiddle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Twiddle) or a more expensive card-drawing variant for surprises when he thinks he'll be playing his big stuff AFTER you activate this ability.",
      "posted_by": "MacBizzle",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost208208\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">This is amazing. Anything that says \"Lose the game next turn\" (not just pacts, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Final Fortune\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Final Fortune\">Final Fortune</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Warrior's Oath\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Warrior's Oath\">Warrior's Oath</a>/<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Last Chance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance\">Last Chance</a>, for example) now says \"Skip a turn\". Anything that says \"lose the game now\" reads \"skip the rest of your second main phase\".<br/><br/>This also might as well read \"1, tap, skip your end step: Exile all opponent's spells.\" Combine with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Twiddle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Twiddle\">Twiddle</a> or a more expensive card-drawing variant for surprises when he thinks he'll be playing his big stuff AFTER you activate this ability.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '208208'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46803\">MacBizzle</span>\r\n                                (11/1/2011 11:33:08 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"p