    {
      "id": "PopularPost175471",
      "post_content": "@Ataogatogatog  \n  \nThis will do what [Time Stop](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Stop) does, i.e. it will exile the counterspell as well as your spell, and any other spells or abilities on the stack.  \n  \nYet another card that lets you play [Phyrexian Dreadnought](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexian Dreadnought) for cheap.  \n  \nI think a more unique combo potential is with negative upkeep abilities that affect all players and a handful of instants or flashy cards. Stuff like [Reality Twist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reality Twist), but less evil.",
      "posted_by": "KikiJikiTiki",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost175471\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">@Ataogatogatog<br/><br/>This will do what <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Time Stop\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Stop\">Time Stop</a> does, i.e. it will exile the counterspell as well as your spell, and any other spells or abilities on the stack.<br/><br/>Yet another card that lets you play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Phyrexian Dreadnought\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexian Dreadnought\">Phyrexian Dreadnought</a> for cheap.<br/><br/>I think a more unique combo potential is with negative upkeep abilities that affect all players and a handful of instants or flashy cards.  Stuff like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reality Twist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reality Twist\">Reality Twist</a>, but less evil.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '175471'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy42642\">KikiJikiTiki</span>\r\n                                (7/7/2011 4:13:12 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<di