      "id": "PopularPost191190",
      "post_content": "I love this card. Why?  \n  \nIt enables you to play [Phage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=40545) as your Commander.   \n  \nYes, [that Phage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=106427). Search for the sundial, play her, then end the turn! Sure, you can also do it with [Platinum Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Platinum Angel), but out of 100 cards, you need as many ways as you can get. Especially since [Stifle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stifle) and [Time Stop](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Stop) aren't black.",
      "posted_by": "Ideatog",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost191190\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I love this card. Why?<br/><br/>It enables you to play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"40545\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=40545\">Phage</a> as your Commander. <br/><br/>Yes, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"106427\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=106427\">that Phage</a>. Search for the sundial, play her, then end the turn! Sure, you can also do it with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Platinum Angel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Platinum Angel\">Platinum Angel</a>, but out of 100 cards, you need as many ways as you can get. Especially since <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stifle\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stifle\">Stifle</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Time Stop\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Time Stop\">Time Stop</a> aren't black.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '191190'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2063\">Ideatog</span>\r\n                                (8/26/2011 12:42:43 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rat